data.description: Charming Home in Ridglea North with tons of updates and beautiful hardwood floors throughout.  Recent updates include: Kitchen- tile backsplash, granite countetops, and stainless appliances. Master bath-updated double vanity and countertop, faucets, oversized shower, and tile floors.  Hall Bath- vanity, sink, faucets, tile floors and tub surround.  Plus Lighting, HVAC in 2017, Low E Windows, and Roof replaced in 2016.  Enjoy entertaining in the large backyard with a spacious back patio.  Plus don't miss the 2 great storage builds, one has electric and makes a great workshop or home office.
